لَفَا فى نُقْطَةٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They two did not differ respecting"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "so small a thing as"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a point"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a letter or word. (TA.) And [hence] the vulgar say, when they admire one,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwa nuqoTapN", "text_ar": "هُوَ نُقْطَةٌ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY muSoHafK", "text_ar": "فِى مُصْحَفٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is like a point,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "stop, in a copy of the Kur-án;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "because the stops in the Kur-án are generally ornamented, and often very beautifully, with gold and colours]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Any very small thing, that may be likened to a point, dot,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "speck."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "Hence,] 'Alee is related to have said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEilomu nuqoTapN A_in~amaA kat~arahaA AljaAhiluwna", "text_ar": "العِلْمُ نُقْطَةٌ اـِنَّمَا كَتَّرَهَا الجَاهِلُونَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Science,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "knowledge, is a very small thing: only the ignorant have made it to be much"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) And you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aEoTaAhu nuqoTapF mino EasalK", "text_ar": "اَعْطَاهُ نُقْطَةً مِنْ عَسَلٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He gave him a drop,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "very small quantity, of honey"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A portion"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a thing, or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "some"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a number of things,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in a separate,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "scattered, state, here and there"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA baqiYa mino", "text_ar": "مَا بَقِىَ مِنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^amowaAlihimo A_il~aA nuqoTapa", "text_ar": "اَمْوَالِهِمْ اـِلَّا نُقْطَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There remained not of their possessions"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[aught]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "save some palm-trees and a portion of seed-produce here and there."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IAar, TA) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY AlA^aroDi niqaATN mina AlkalaA_i", "text_ar": "فِى الاَرْضِ نِقَاطٌ مِنَ الكَلَاـِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nuqaTN minohu", "text_ar": "نُقَطٌ مِنْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "In the land are scattered spots,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "portions, of herbage."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, * TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing: an affair; a matter: a case; an event; an action."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["K", "TA", "S", "Msb", "IAar"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}